%p Search and Sort

%p
  ElectricCourage users post flirty messages to a common event wall, 
  but also like to search the wall to see if someone mentioned them.
  Given a list of wall posts and a query, implement a search 
  that will return the relevant post ids.
  %br
  You are given: 1. an list containing data about posts; 2. a query string.
  Return the number of posts that contain the query string, followed by 
  a list of the ids of matching posts, sorted in order by date posted.  
  Ignore case.

