%h4 Posts
.data
  %code
    \# id (string) <br>
    \# time (int) <br>
    \# message (string) <br>
    1<br>
    1321046427<br>
    chocolate gumdrops<br>
    2<br>
    1321046425<br>
    honey popsicle<br>
    3<br>
    1321046422<br>
    Chocolate ice cream
%h4 Query
